  "prompt": "Which are the good CA coaching centres in south Delhi?",
  "response": "There are several reputable CA coaching centers in South Delhi. Here are some of the well-known ones:\n\n1. **Vidya Sagar Classes** - Known for its structured programs and experienced faculty, Vidya Sagar is a popular choice among CA aspirants.\n\n2. **CA Ravi Agarwal Classes** - Offers a range of CA courses and is known for its comprehensive study material and expert faculty.\n\n3. **ACCA and CA Institute** - They provide coaching for various levels and have a good track record of student success.\n\n4. **EduPristine** - Offers CA coaching with a focus on practical training and includes various study materials and resources.\n\n5. **Prakash S. Tax Consultancy and CA Academy** - Known for its focused training approach and personalized attention to students.\n\n6. **Godfrey Phillips Academy** - Offers CA coaching with a focus on interactive learning and mentorship.\n\n7. **Cramster** - Provides online and offline coaching for CA exams, focusing on exam strategies and practice.\n\n8. **Niraj Agarwal Classes** - Well-regarded for its experienced faculty and detailed study materials.\n\nWhen choosing a coaching center, consider factors like faculty experience, student reviews, class timings, support for doubt clearing, and success rates to find the best fit for your needs. It's also a good idea to visit the centers if possible and attend a demo class before making a decision.",
